 - Yeah.

263
00:17:56,630 --> 00:17:59,400
I charge 300,000 won?

264
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:02,920
It'd be the value of the major law firm title you have,

265
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:05,420
not you as the individual, right?

