00:18:09,170 --> 00:18:14,780
I also know our partner attorneys charge 500,000 won per hour.

268
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:20,270
By the way, what does "JS" stand for?

269
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:21,930
They're special markings I made.

270
00:18:21,930 --> 00:18:23,730
