00:33:44,740 --> 00:33:47,580
He brought it upon himself.

512
00:33:47,580 --> 00:33:54,150
Still, I just wonder who'd take care of him when he gets old.

513
00:33:55,390 --> 00:34:01,000
You're not the only one with responsibility and duty.

514
00:34:01,610 --> 00:34:05,070
Do you think the defendant will take care of you when you get sick?

515
00:34:05,070 --> 00:34:06,950
My gosh...

516
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:11,150
He made you sick, in fact.

517
00:34:13,090 --> 00:34:17,350
Only if I hadn't told him about meeting you.

518
00:34:17,350 --> 00:34:21,420
I think it's kind of right to stop now while I can.

519
00:34:21,870 --> 00:34:26,960
If you're that worried, give my number to your husband

