00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,740
and tell him to talk to me.

521
00:34:28,740 --> 00:34:32,550
And you can just block your husband's number.

522
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:34,490
Please do it right now.

523
00:34:36,380 --> 00:34:37,770
Can I really do that?

