00:34:37,770 --> 00:34:39,780
Of course.

525
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:47,380
 Husband  
  I'm not going home. 

526
00:34:47,380 --> 00:34:50,660
 You can talk to my attorney now if you want to contact me. 

527
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:54,350
He'll go crazy if he can't even reach me.

528
00:34:54,350 --> 00:34:55,760
It's fine.

529
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:58,740
I told you to trust me and let me lead you.

530
00:35:03,530 --> 00:35:06,400
This is Park Jin Suk's past consultation notes you mentioned.

531
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,440
Thank you.

532
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:12,160
 010-0825-5183 

